WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:04.000 
[Hissing]
00:04.000 --> 00:07.000 
[tape recorder click]
00:07.000 --> 00:09.000 
I do not remember launch day
00:09.000 --> 00:12.000 
We must have entered orbit
00:12.000 --> 00:13.000 
for I do remember
00:13.000 --> 00:15.000 
the thrill of microgravity
00:15.000 --> 00:17.000 
the others around me
00:17.000 --> 00:19.000 
above me
00:19.000 --> 00:21.000 
all of us feeling naked
00:21.000 --> 00:22.000 
inside our carapaces
00:22.000 --> 00:25.000 
drifting against the walls or our shells. 
00:25.000 --> 00:27.000 
[tape recorder click]


